title: Footy Quiz — Test your AFL knowledge | The
text:
HOW well do you know footy?
Every week during the 2015 season you can test your knowledge with eight quick questions.
Footy history buff? That might help. Have a secret footy card collection? That should get you off to a good start.
Keep a close eye on the body art of AFL stars? Now you’re in business.
Start the quiz below — then challenge your mates.
Fun Friday Footy Quiz (Frame content direct link: http://media.heraldsun.com.au/multimedia/2015/apr/top_eight/QUIZ_12/quiz12.html .)
